      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 6 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 6 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二，不克訟，歸而逋，其邑人三百戶无眚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject unequal to the contention. If he retire and keep concealed (where) the inhabitants of his city are (only) three hundred families, he will fall into no mistake.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-006-song__alignment-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">yijing</prop>
