      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 6 六三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 6 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三，食舊德，貞厲，終吉。或從王事，无成。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows its subject keeping in the old place assigned for his support, and firmly correct. Perilous as the position is, there will be good fortune in the end. Should he perchance engage in the king's business, he will not (claim the merit of) achievement.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
