      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 6 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 6 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四，不克訟，復即命渝，安貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject unequal to the contention. He returns to (the study of Heaven's) ordinances, changes (his wish to contend), and rests in being firm and correct. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
