      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 6 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五，訟，元吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>S. The fifth NINE, undivided, shows its subject contending - and with great good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
