      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 6 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 6 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九，或錫之鞶帶，終朝三褫之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost NINE, undivided, shows how its subject may have the leathern belt conferred on him (by the sovereign), and thrice it shall be taken from him in a morning.</seg>
      </tuv>
